Neurotic Haze is a common battle [[Bog Parasites|Bog-Parasite]] for [[Rook]], it costs 1 action and has the effect: "Discard 2 random cards from your hand and gain 2 actions. Parasite, Hatch"

==Hatch==
When Neurotic Haze hatches, it is transformed into a random uncommon battle Bog Parasite, so [[Branch]], [[Delirium]] or [[Fever]].